    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">Index XXVIII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index XVIIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXVII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXVII. de Ioannis Corvini et sancti Ioannis Capistrani pio obitu</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Paucis post <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B"><app>
                                <lem wit="#KK">ab</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B"><add type="insert">ab</add></rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#P"/>
                            </app> adepta victoria</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">adeptam victoriam</rdg>
                    </app><!--ellenőrizendő  --> diebus incidit Corvinus in morbum gravissimum, quem
                    contraxit ob nimium laborem, quem in re gerenda susceperat.</s>
                <s n="2">Iam enim advenerat tempus, quo pro magnis suis in Christianam pietatem
                    meritis esset in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">caelo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coelo</rdg>
                    </app> sua praemia consecuturus.</s>
                <s n="3">Cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">autem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">vero</rdg>
                    </app> morbi vis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">vehementer</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">vaehementer</rdg>
                    </app> invalesceret, ipso iubente delatus est ad oppidum, quod <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Zemplem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Zemplen</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Zemplén</rdg>
                    </app> Hungarorum lingua appellatur, fecisse id se dixit, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">eo in</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">in eo</rdg>
                    </app> loco deo spiritum suum redderet longe quietius.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">1–3 = Th 4.56.</note></s>
                <s n="4">Eo Capistranus profectus, ut amici religiosique viri uteretur <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">officio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">offitio</rdg>
                    </app>, adhortari eum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #M">coepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">caepit</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">cepit</rdg>
                    </app>, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1">(cum nihil spei de ipsius vitae salute
                            superesset)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum nihil spei de ipsius vitae salute
                            superesset</rdg>
                    </app> ne <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">differat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">differet</rdg>
                    </app> ulterius, quo minus Christianorum ritu suscipiat sacramenta, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> Christiani homines solent in extremo vitae constituti suscipere.</s>
                <s n="5">Mirari se ille respondit religiosi viri prudentiam, qui moneat <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">moriendum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">monendum</rdg>
                    </app> Christiane virum, qui pro Christiana fide dimicando persaepe sese morti
                    exposuerit, igitur si nescivit antehac, sciat nunc eum semper, dum fuit in vita
                    in aetate virili, se et putasse peccatorem et cogitasse moriturum, idcirco
                    perdiu se hoc servasse, ut peccatorum confessionem nunquam ultra mensem
                    distulerit, non ergo se nunc <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">expectasse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exspectasse</rdg>
                    </app> moriendi momentum, sed more Christiani viri se ordinasse prudenter,
                    quaecunque vel ad animae suae salutem vel ad filios, quos relinquebat, atque ad
                    facultates <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S3 #M">ceterasque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2">caeterasque</rdg>
                    </app> res domesticas suas vel ad rem publicam totius Hungarici regni, quam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">multos annos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">multis annis</rdg>
                    </app> administraverat, pertinerent, nec sibi reliquum esse aliud, quam ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sumat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">summat</rdg>
                    </app> eucharistiam suoque deinde tempore unctionis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">extremae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">externae</rdg>
                    </app> sacramentum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">ut ita</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ubi ita</rdg>
                    </app> fecerit, se non indiguisse mortalis alicuius sed solum dei et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #M">domini sui</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">domini nostri</rdg>
                    </app> Iesu Christi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">consilii</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">consilio</rdg>
                    </app>, cuius nomen et cultum ipse in omni <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sua vita</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">vita sua</rdg>
                    </app> adversus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">blasfemantes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">blasfemantem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">blasphemantem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">blasphemantes</rdg>
                    </app> illum Turcas multis bellis variisque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #M">proeliis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">preliis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3">praeliis</rdg>
                    </app> defendisset, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">autem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">vero</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">ageret cuncta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cuncta ageret</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae nunc</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que nunc</rdg>
                    </app> commemorat, eo mortalem quempiam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">se noluisse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">noluisse se</rdg>
                    </app> consulere, quod servanda sibi fuerit sui illa existimatio et auctoritas,
                    qua maxime valuisset apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">universas</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">universos</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2">paene</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">pene</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">prene</rdg>
                    </app> Christianas nationes, nequaquam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">enim</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">cũ</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">decuisse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">condecuisse</rdg>
                    </app> virum, qui dum vixit, professus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">tutatusque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">tutusque</rdg>
                    </app> sit catholicam pietatem, alterius eguisse persuasione, quo bene pieque
                    vita <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">excederet</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">excaederet</rdg>
                    </app>, satis igitur <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">superque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #M">supraque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">se fuisse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fuisse se</rdg>
                    </app> a seipso persuasum, ut mori velit ritu Christiano.</s>
                <s n="6">His mox <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">haec</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2"/>
                    </app> adiecit:</s>
                <s n="7">Gratias nihilominus tibi ago immortales, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ioannes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Ioan-<note type="critic">fol. sequens deperditum
                            est</note></rdg>
                    </app><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"> mi pater in Christo <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">carissime</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">charissime</rdg>
                            </app>, qui religiosi <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">viri in me</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">in me viri</rdg>
                            </app> officio <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">tanta</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#M">tanto</rdg>
                            </app>
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">usus es</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">es usus</rdg>
                            </app> humanitate, bono animo esto, domum, unde huc te contulisti, redi,
                            spero equidem illic te auditurum Ioannem Corvinum Christiane suum <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">obivisse</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L2">obiisse</rdg>
                            </app> diem.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"/>
                    </app></s>
                <app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">
                        <s n="8">Capistrano <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">discedente</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">dicente</rdg>
                            </app> multis, qui aderant e regni proceribus, quos secum duxerat in
                            expeditionem, quae modo memorata est, patefacit, quaecunque <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">ipse</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ille</rdg>
                            </app> disposuerat testamento a se iam condito, priusquam Belgradum
                            eiusdem belli causa proficisceretur.</s>
                        <s n="9">Vernacula lingua prolixam tunc habuit orationem, qua omnes est
                            cohortatus, ut suo exemplo Christianam primum fidem, deinde Hungarici
                            regni rem publicam a Turcarum rabie atque ab omni alio hostili <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">incursu</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#M">insultu</rdg>
                            </app> defenderent, suasit, ut procul ab illorum animis esset discordia,
                            cui si studuerint, et se perditum irent et fore, ut omne regnum eorum
                            sine ulla dubitatione deleatur, cunctis quidem sed illis praecipue,
                            quibus vivens fuerat usus familiarius, commendavit rem suam domesticam,
                            liberos <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praesertim</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#P">presertim</rdg>
                            </app> et coniugem, consanguineos praeterea et <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #S3 #M">ceteros</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2">caeteros</rdg>
                            </app>, qui ei fuerant <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">benivolentia</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">benevolentia</rdg>
                            </app> coniuncti.</s>
                        <s n="10">Facto dicendi fine singulos suo appellatos nomine ad se ire
                            voluit, dataque dextera <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R">dextrae</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">dextre</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="M"/>
                            </app> illos exosculatus est, nemo ex illis fuit, qui non fleverit <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">lachrymis</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1">lachrimis</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#M">lacrymis</rdg>
                            </app>
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">huberrimis</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">uberrimis</rdg>
                            </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">4–10 = Th 4.56, sed haec
                                tantum: „in recommendatione praefati fratris Ioannis de Capistrano,
                                viri dei, suo salvatori suum restituit spiritum“; cetera Ransani
                                sunt.</note></s>
                        <s n="11">Mira profecto memoratuque digna <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">ea</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illa</rdg>
                            </app> fuere, at vero non sunt praetereunda silentio duo alia a se
                            praebita Christianissimi hominis exempla.</s>
                    </lem>
                    <rdg wit="#B"/>
                </app>
                <s n="12"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Unum, quod noluit pati, ut
                            eucharistia <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ab</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#P">ad</rdg>
                            </app> ecclesia ad se deferretur, indignum ducens domum usque suam mundi <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2">redemptorem</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">redemtorem</rdg>
                            </app>, qui in eo lateret sacramento, <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">accedere</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#P">accaedere</rdg>
                            </app>, <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">quanquam</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #M">quamquam</rdg>
                            </app> non ignorabat posse id fieri pro aegrotantium necessitate, licet
                            igitur gravaretur vi maxima morbi, pedibus tamen suis quamvis <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">iutus a domesticis</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illis aegris</rdg>
                            </app>
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">sacram</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#M">sacrum</rdg>
                            </app> adiit aedem, ubi obortis <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">lachrymis</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#M">lacrymis</rdg>
                            </app></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">miraque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">miraque<note type="critic">B textus redintegratur, fol.
                                anterior deperditum est</note></rdg>
                    </app> pietate Christi corpus veneratus eucharistiam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R">sumpsit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sumsit</rdg>
                    </app>, domumque dehinc incredibili mentis gaudio <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L1">laeticiaque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">laetitiaque</rdg>
                    </app> affectus regressus est.<note type="critic">11–12 cf. Aeneas Sylvius:
                            <title>Europa</title> cap. 1. - Etiamsi Ransanus hoc opus in manibus non
                        habuisset, tamen homines litterati id ubique versabant, ille etiam ex
                        memoria afferre potuisset. Credi potest etiam Aeneam et Ransanum materiam ex
                        eodem sermone sumpsisse. Index XXVIII.13–15 narratiunculam ab Aenea haud
                        memoratam continens hanc existimationem confirmare videtur.</note></s>
                <s n="13">Alterum hoc fuit:</s>
                <s n="14"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Accepta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">Accaepta</rdg>
                    </app> extrema unctione, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">quom</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum</rdg>
                    </app> primum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">animadvertit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">anima advertit</rdg>
                    </app> se iam morti propinquum, portari se <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">voluit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">iussit</rdg>
                    </app> ad sacellum, quod ipse <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">condiderat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R">condidcrat</rdg>
                    </app>, ubi mortuus erat sepeliendus, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3">ibi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #M">ubi</rdg>
                    </app> iussit se extenso supinoque corpore humi collocari, succendi praeterea
                    collocarique voluit ad caput ac pedes aliquot lumina, ut consuetum est in
                    defunctorum fieri corporibus, antequam tumulentur.</s>
                <s n="15"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Expectandum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">Exspectandum</rdg>
                    </app> autem ibidem tantisper a quatuor ordinis minorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">clericis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">cloericis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">claericis</rdg>
                    </app>, a quibus sacri psalmi dicerentur, dum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extingueretur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstingueretur</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="16">Eo moriente affuit Capistranus, a quo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">perlectae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">perlecte</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">perfectae</rdg>
                    </app> sunt orationes <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ille</rdg>
                    </app>, quas sancti Christiani patres legi constituerunt, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">quom</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #L2">qui</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quum</rdg>
                    </app> Christi fideles mortis horae propinquant, vulgata autem appellatione <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">nuncupatur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">nuncupantur</rdg>
                    </app> commendatio <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">animae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">anime</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="17">Postea vero, quam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extinctus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstinctus</rdg>
                    </app> est, his in eum usus fuisse verbis Capistranus fertur:</s>
                <s n="18">Vale, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">caeleste</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coeleste</rdg>
                    </app> sidus, heu, cecidisti defensor Christianorum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extincta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstincta</rdg>
                    </app> est lucerna Christiani orbis, heu, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fractum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">factum</rdg>
                    </app> est speculum, in quod <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">intuentes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">intuens</rdg>
                    </app> Christiani propugnatores non dubitabant de assequenda victoria!</s>
                <s n="19"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app>, bone Ioannes, tecum bene actum est, nam superato hoste nominis
                    Christiani <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">triumphas</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">tryumphas</rdg>
                    </app> cum angelis et regnas in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">caelo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">celo</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coelo</rdg>
                    </app> cum Christo, tu igitur vere <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">felix</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #L1">foelix</rdg>
                    </app> es, nos <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">infelices</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #L1">infoelices</rdg>
                    </app>, qui relinquimur in hac valle <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">lachrymarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">lachrimarum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">lacrymarum</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="20">O, bone Ioannes, aeternum vale!</s>
                <s n="21">Ingenti ob tanti viri obitum dolore atque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">maestitia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">moestitia</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">moesticia</rdg>
                    </app> affecti sunt non solum universi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">totius Hungariae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Hungariae totius</rdg>
                    </app> populi sed omnes <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quoque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">queque</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">quaeque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">Christiani orbis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">orbis Christiani</rdg>
                    </app> nationes, luxit eum Nicolaus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #M">quintus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">V.</rdg>
                    </app> pontifex maximus omnisque Romana curia, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tam fortem tamque fortunatum ac pium <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Christianae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1">Christiane</rdg>
                    </app> religionis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">defensorem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">defensornm</rdg>
                    </app> amisit, pontificis iussu cardinalium senatus ei magnifice persolvit
                    inferias.</s>
                <s n="22">Ei <app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L2">solennitati</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">solemnitati</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">solennitatiti</rdg>
                    </app> ipse interfui.</s>
                <s n="23">Eius obitum visum est <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">caelum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coelum</rdg>
                    </app> universo orbi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">terrarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">tetrarum</rdg>
                    </app> significasse.</s>
                <s n="24">Crinitum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sidus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R">sydus</rdg>
                    </app>, quem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">cometen</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #M">cometem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">cometam</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Graeci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Greci</rdg>
                    </app> vocant, aliquot, antequam incideret in adversam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">valitudinem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">valetudinem</rdg>
                    </app>, diebus ab orientali apparuit plaga, quem ut ipse vidit, domesticis dixit
                    eo indicio multa quidem alia significari sed obitum praecipue suum, ideoque non
                    esse sibi morandum diutius, sed dandam operam, ut disponat domui suae, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">expectetque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exspectetque</rdg>
                    </app> vigilanter diem et horam, qua ipsum deus mortali vita eripiat.</s>
                <s n="25">Nec secus, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2">praenunciaverat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">prenunciaverat</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praenuntiaverat</rdg>
                    </app>, evenit, paucis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> diebus, postquam evanuit cometes, invasit eum morbus, quo sublatum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B"><app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fuisse</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2"/>
                            </app> ipsum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ipsum fuisse</rdg>
                    </app> ostendimus.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">16–25 = Th 4.56. – 22 <hi
                            rend="italic">Ei solennitati ipse interfui</hi> – attamen falso
                        scribitur, nam Nicolaus V. anno superiore mortuus est. Thuróczy enim ea,
                        quae apud Belgradum gesta sunt, annum 1455 adscribit, Ransanus autem,
                        quamquam anni numerum non notat, sane in errore inducitur. De sollemniis
                        triumphi v. epistulam Calixti III. ad Carolum regem Franciae (10. Aug.
                        1456.), in qua regem ea occasione sacra facere petit (Georgius Pray:
                            <title>Annales regum Hungariae</title>. Vol. III. Vindobonae 1768. 184),
                        Nicolaus autem Severinus 13. Aug. pontificem maximum campanas Romae pulsare
                        pompamque sollemnem instituere nunciat. (Pastor: <title>Geschichte der
                            Päpste</title>. Bd. I. Anhang, 72.)</note></s>
                <s n="26">Paucis autem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">post diebus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">„diebus“ post</rdg>
                    </app> diem suum et Capistranus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">obivit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">obiit</rdg>
                    </app>, ut virum dei servum decuit.<note type="critic">P textus Epithomatis
                        finitur, sequitur <quote>Annalium omnium temporum liber XLIIII. finit et
                            XLV. incipit foeliciter. Anno a Iesu Christi ortu quarto et quadragesimo
                            supra mille et quadringentos haec fuisse gesta memoratu digna ad meam
                            pervenere noticiam. Alfonsus rex urbem Neapolim triumphans ingreditur...
                            [etc.]</quote></note><note type="critic" corresp="RKK">26 = Th
                        4.37.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
